<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/beyond-the-economic-chaos-of-coronavirus-is-a-global-war-economy/">Beyond the Economic Chaos of Coronavirus Is a Global War Economy</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">In the face of excessive capital accumulation, war and repression have become profit centers for the capitalist class.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/william-i-robinson/" itemprop="url" rel="author">William I. Robinson</a></span>, </dd>
